    <Entry>
      <ID>49</ID>
      <DefaultText>"Queenslayer!" Her blade is immediately freed from its sheath. "Mouthpiece of [url=glossary:kyros]Kyros[/url]!" She thrusts the sword into the air. "Tiersmen, rally! This cur would take [url=glossary:vendrien's well]Vendrien's Well[/url] and consign us all to death! Run the whore-mouth through!"</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>50</ID>
      <DefaultText>"The Fatebinder." She slides her weapon from its sheath and holds it aloft. "Tiersmen, this is the tyrant who would take our lands from us. Who would claim the citadel. Who would damn us all to death." She lowers the blade's point towards you. "I know none more deserving of death than this one."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
